Dialogs.Text: SecurPink1850: So, what is your group exactly?
MsMaki95: We are interested in lost software, movies and many other things. ^-^
MsMaki95: Things that people remember existed, but can't be found anymore. u-u
SecurPink1850: You are like a lost and found group, then.
MsMaki95: That's a cold way to put it but, yes. o-o
SecurPink1850: Why do you do it?
MsMaki95: It's interesting, you find something new every day. And well, it feels like recording history. c:
Thomas B: Basically, people with a lot of free time.
MsMaki95: You seem like a curious guy, i think they will love to include you in the team if you meet them. n-n
SecurPink1850: Sounds interesting, but i will have to think about it.
Thomas B: Note to myself, i have to be more relaxed with the way i ask questions.

Elections.CandidateName: When did you join the server?
